name: Defidash
description: Defidash Agent provides real time trading automation on X and Telegram. Additionally, Defidash provides real time market analytics utilizing over 40 AI data feeds. Defidash Agent is designed to learn from its environment and past actions, which means it can improve over time. This adaptation can lead to better trading outcomes and more efficient management of crypto assets. DeFiDash answers the call for an adaptive, insightful, and secure environment to monitor and manage digital assets.
